page.title: 12Life Styles-A Hemsworth Girl
page.content: There are three of us in the family,me ,my mum and my dad.We live on a maisonette on Gaunt Rd. In our house we have a lot of pets;a cross Red setter/Collie,two goldfish,a budgerigar and two mice.Every night we take our dog over the local golf course for a walk. Our house has two bedrooms a kitchen,a living-room, and a bathroom with a toilet.The maisonettes are pebble-dashed to insulate them.We have a silver coloured Ford car and a garage to keep it in.When we go on holiday we nearly always go somewhere with amusements for the children.We have been to Butlins Holiday Camp at Pwllheli in Wales for about three years because the children like it.
